## Reactivate your account

### If you work in a government department or arm's length body

Ask an organisation admin or managing editor in your organisation to unsuspend your account in Signon.

### If you are an organisation admin or managing editor

Ask another organisation admin or managing editor in your organisation to unsuspend you.

Admins in an arm's length body may need an editor from their parent organisation to unsuspend accounts.

### If you work in a local authority

Contact licensing-authorities@digital.cabinet-office.gov.uk to reactivate your account if you work in a local council.
